<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 04:10:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“我们是由愚蠢的人统治的”：特朗普呼吁修改宪法以罢免“密谋”副总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/were-run-by-stupid-people-trump-calls-for-constitutional-change-to-remove-conspiring-vice-presidents/articleshow/113160223.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160223.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普提议修改第25条修正案，罢免掩盖总统无能的副总统。这一呼吁是在威斯康星州的一次竞选集会上做出的，是为了回应乔·拜登糟糕的辩论表现以及随后退出总统竞选，卡马拉·哈里斯因此成为民主党提名人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/were-run-by-stupid-people-trump-calls-for-constitutional-change-to-remove-conspiring-vice-presidents/articleshow/113160223.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国圣贝纳迪诺气温突破三位数，肆虐的野火迫使人们疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/raging-wildfire-forces-evacuations-in-us-san-bernardino-as-temperatures-cross-triple-digits/articleshow/113160573.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160573.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;洛杉矶附近的圣贝纳迪诺国家森林发生野火，气温高达 112°F，导致人员疏散。星期四晚上发生的线火已经烧毁了 11 平方英里的植被。超过 500 名消防员在空中支援下赶赴现场。官员警告说，未来 12 小时内火势可能会严重蔓延。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/raging-wildfire-forces-evacuations-in-us-san-bernardino-as-temperatures-cross-triple-digits/articleshow/113160573.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国认为伊朗已向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia/articleshow/113160521.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160521.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国认为伊朗已向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹用于乌克兰战争，引发了对冲突升级和欧洲安全威胁的担忧。白宫重申对此类转让的警告，而伊朗则否认提供武器，并呼吁停火。中央情报局局长强调了涉及俄罗斯、中国、伊朗和朝鲜的令人不安的防务关系。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia/articleshow/113160521.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡玛拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普将在首场辩论中对决：规则是什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-and-donald-trump-to-face-off-in-first-debate-what-are-the-rules/articleshow/113160440.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160440.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡马拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普将于 9 月 10 日进行首次直接辩论。这场辩论由 ABC 新闻在费城国家宪法中心主办，时长 90 分钟，包括定时回答和静音麦克风，以确保辩论顺利进行。辩论将在全国范围内转播，没有现场观众。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-and-donald-trump-to-face-off-in-first-debate-what-are-the-rules/articleshow/113160440.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 透露了 SpaceX 将无人驾驶星际飞船送往火星的雄心勃勃的计划：我们所知道的</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-reveals-spacexs-ambitious-plan-to-send-uncrewed-starships-to-mars-what-we-know/articleshow/113160287.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160287.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃隆·马斯克宣布，SpaceX 将在两年内向火星发射第一艘无人驾驶星际飞船，旨在测试其着陆可靠性。如果成功，载人任务将在四年内进行。最终目标是在大约 20 年内在火星上建立一座自给自足的城市。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-reveals-spacexs-ambitious-plan-to-send-uncrewed-starships-to-mars-what-we-know/articleshow/113160287.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗特勤局特工因在欧洲范围内密谋杀害犹太人而在法国被拘留</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iranian-secret-service-agents-detained-in-france-for-europe-wide-plot-to-kill-jews/articleshow/113160024.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160024.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Abdelkrim S 和 Sabrina B 因涉嫌参与伊朗支持的针对德国和法国犹太人的暗杀阴谋而受到巴黎一家法院的指控。这对夫妇被指控与恐怖组织合谋，目前被审前拘留。调查还将其与对以色列企业的纵火企图联系起来。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iranian-secret-service-agents-detained-in-france-for-europe-wide-plot-to-kill-jews/articleshow/113160024.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国肯塔基州高速公路多人遭枪击，追捕“武装”嫌疑人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/multiple-people-shot-along-highway-in-us-state-of-kentucky-hunt-for-armed-suspect-on/articleshow/113159936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113159936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在肯塔基州南部，75 号州际公路的一段路段因枪击事件而关闭，造成多人受伤。当局正在寻找嫌疑人约瑟夫·库奇，他被认为携带武器且危险。劳雷尔县治安官办公室和肯塔基州警方建议居民在追捕嫌疑人期间留在室内。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:21:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/multiple-people-shot-along-highway-in-us-state-of-kentucky-hunt-for-armed-suspect-on/articleshow/113159936.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击案嫌疑人柯尔特·格雷在案发前曾住在几处出租房中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-colt-gray-lived-in-several-rental-homes-prior-to-the-incident/articleshow/113159693.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113159693.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 14 岁犯罪嫌疑人柯尔特·格雷 (Colt Gray) 和他的父亲科林 (Colin) 因在佐治亚州阿巴拉奇高中杀害两名学生和两名教师而面临指控。科林离婚后，一家人多次搬家。柯尔特饱受欺凌和父母分居的困扰。他因这起事件而作为成年人接受审判。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 00:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-colt-gray-lived-in-several-rental-homes-prior-to-the-incident/articleshow/113159693.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子将在 40 岁后获得主要遗产。他将得到......</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-set-to-receive-major-inheritance-after-he-turns-40-he-will-get-/articleshow/113157399.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157399.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈里王子将于 9 月 15 日庆祝他的 40 岁生日，他将从一个家庭信托基金中收到约 800 万英镑。该基金由他的曾祖母于 1994 年设立，旨在为她的曾孙提供经济礼物。通过与 Spotify、Netflix 的交易和图书合同，这对夫妇的财富不断增加，财务上的增长也随之增加。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-set-to-receive-major-inheritance-after-he-turns-40-he-will-get-/articleshow/113157399.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国MQ-9无人机在也门马里布省被胡塞武装击落</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-mq-9-drone-shot-down-by-houthis-in-yemens-marib-governorate/articleshow/113157558.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157558.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;与伊朗结盟的胡塞组织声称对击落也门马里卜省上空的一架美国 MQ-9 无人机负责，称该无人机正在进行敌对活动。这一事件与胡塞武装在红海和亚丁湾持续袭击船只有关，因为他们要求结束加沙的以色列与哈马斯冲突。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-mq-9-drone-shot-down-by-houthis-in-yemens-marib-governorate/articleshow/113157558.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击事件：欺凌和家庭斗争如何导致四人死亡的悲剧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-how-bullying-and-family-struggles-led-to-tragedy-that-killed-four/articleshow/113158183.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113158183.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名 14 岁男孩和他的父亲因在佐治亚州阿巴拉奇高中发生致命枪击事件而面临指控，该枪击案造成四人死亡。此案凸显了这名少年的家庭生活陷入困境、持续受到欺凌，以及他父亲在让他获得枪支方面所扮演的角色。两人于 2023 年 9 月首次出庭。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 22:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-how-bullying-and-family-struggles-led-to-tragedy-that-killed-four/articleshow/113158183.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦陆军参谋长首次承认其在 1999 年卡吉尔战争中发挥了直接作用</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pak-army-admits-involvement-in-kargil-war/articleshow/113156851.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113156851.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦陆军总司令阿西姆·穆尼尔 (Asim Munir) 将军承认，巴基斯坦军队直接参与了 1999 年针对印度的卡吉尔战争，结束了长期以来只有克什米尔本土叛军参与战斗的说法。他向在冲突中阵亡的巴基斯坦士兵致敬，并承认他们在之前的战争中为国家和伊斯兰教做出的牺牲。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 18:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pak-army-admits-involvement-in-kargil-war/articleshow/113156851.cms</guid></item><item><title>一位街头艺术家记录了乌克兰的战争，一次一幅鲜明的壁画</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-street-artist-documents-war-in-ukraine-one-stark-mural-at-a-time/articleshow/113157179.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157179.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰街头艺术家 Gamlet Zinkivskyi 加入了一支保卫哈尔科夫的志愿部队，但他的指挥官建议他改为绘画。他在被炸毁的街道上创作的壁画描绘了战时现实，鼓舞了士兵和平民的士气。尽管受到广泛赞赏，但他的一些作品因其主题而受到批评。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-street-artist-documents-war-in-ukraine-one-stark-mural-at-a-time/articleshow/113157179.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦男子因涉嫌密谋于 10 月 7 日左右袭击纽约市犹太中心而受到指控</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pakistani-man-charged-over-alleged-plot-to-attack-new-york-city-jewish-centre-around-october-7/articleshow/113157164.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157164.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;居住在加拿大的巴基斯坦公民穆罕默德·沙泽布·汗因策划袭击纽约市的一个犹太中心而被捕。这次袭击定于 2024 年 10 月举行，旨在杀害尽可能多的支持伊斯兰国的犹太人。如果罪名成立，汗将面临最高20年的监禁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:38:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pakistani-man-charged-over-alleged-plot-to-attack-new-york-city-jewish-centre-around-october-7/articleshow/113157164.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击案嫌疑人因家庭破碎而困扰，他的父亲说，他在学校受到嘲笑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-was-troubled-by-a-broken-family-taunting-at-school-his-father-said/articleshow/113157138.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157138.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;科林·格雷和他十几岁的儿子柯尔特被指控杀害阿巴拉奇高中的两名学生和两名教师。柯尔特被指控谋杀，而科林则面临提供武器的指控。一年前的一次驱逐导致分居，一家人陷入困境，影响了柯尔特的精神状态。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-was-troubled-by-a-broken-family-taunting-at-school-his-father-said/articleshow/113157138.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰：德黑兰和莫斯科之间的军事合作对欧洲和西亚构成威胁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/military-cooperation-between-tehran-and-moscow-a-threat-to-europe-west-asia-ukraine/articleshow/113157108.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157108.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰外交部对伊朗可能向俄罗斯转让弹道导弹表示担忧，认为这对乌克兰、欧洲和中东构成威胁。该部呼吁加大对两国的国际压力。有报道称，伊朗已经向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹，加剧了当前冲突的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:28:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/military-cooperation-between-tehran-and-moscow-a-threat-to-europe-west-asia-ukraine/articleshow/113157108.cms</guid></item><item><title>希拉里·克林顿对辩论唐纳德·特朗普提出建议：“他可能会感到不安”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hillary-clinton-has-advice-on-debating-donald-trump-he-can-be-rattled/articleshow/113157085.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157085.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;希拉里·克林顿 (Hillary Clinton) 在 2016 年大选中与唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 辩论方面经验丰富，为卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 的辩论策略提供了指导。克林顿强调，特朗普避免直接回答，缺乏具体细节。她建议哈里斯通过实质性攻击来暴露特朗普的领导缺陷，这可能会引起选民对其稳定性的怀疑。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 19:23:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hillary-clinton-has-advice-on-debating-donald-trump-he-can-be-rattled/articleshow/113157085.cms</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局和军情六处负责人罕见地联合呼吁加沙停火</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/in-rare-move-heads-of-cia-mi6-issue-joint-call-for-ceasefire-in-gaza/articleshow/113148437.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113148437.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中央情报局局长威廉·伯恩斯和军情六处局长理查德·摩尔呼吁加沙停火，以缓和以色列与哈马斯的冲突。他们强调他们的情报工作是为了斡旋和平并结束平民苦难。首脑们还讨论了来自俄罗斯、中国和恐怖主义的全球威胁，同时赞扬乌克兰抵御俄罗斯侵略的能力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:40:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/in-rare-move-heads-of-cia-mi6-issue-joint-call-for-ceasefire-in-gaza/articleshow/113148437.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦旁遮普省挫败重大恐怖袭击事件，逮捕30多名恐怖分子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/major-terror-attack-foiled-over-30-terrorists-arrested-in-punjab-province-of-pakistan/articleshow/113150312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113150312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦旁遮普省执法机构逮捕了包括基地组织在内的多个被禁组织的33名恐怖分子，挫败了一起重大恐怖阴谋。反恐部门在不同地区开展了 475 次基于情报的行动，审问嫌疑人并收缴武器和爆炸物。针对被拘留者的案件已立案。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 10:47:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/major-terror-attack-foiled-over-30-terrorists-arrested-in-punjab-province-of-pakistan/articleshow/113150312.cms</guid></item><item><title>超强台风八木袭击越南：造成大范围破坏，至少四人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/super-typhoon-yagi-hits-vietnam-at-least-four-killed-amid-widespread-destruction/articleshow/113152083.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113152083.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;超强台风“八木”袭击越南北部，造成至少四人死亡和广泛破坏。台风将树木连根拔起，船只移位，房屋屋顶被掀翻。由于预计会发生灾难，当局将数千名居民疏散到更安全的地区。在袭击越南之前，它在中国南部和菲律宾留下了破坏痕迹。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 12:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/super-typhoon-yagi-hits-vietnam-at-least-four-killed-amid-widespread-destruction/articleshow/113152083.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>